HEADWORD: Ayuntamiento
<hw>A*yun`ta*mi*en"to</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.,
fr. OSp. <ets>ayuntar</ets> to join.]</ety> <def>In Spain and Spanish
